XOR ENCRYPTION

( ^ is XOR )

XOR is Exclusive OR- or only "1" if only one key is "on"

How we do it?
input          :    0 < c < 256              0 1 1 0
Secret Key     :    0 < k < 256            ^ 1 1 0 0
Encrypted char :    c' = c ^ k             ---------
Decrpytion     :    c  = c' ^ k              1 0 1 0

  (b ^ 0) ^ 0
 = b

  (b ^ 1) ^ 1
= (1 - b) ^ 1
= 1 - (1 - b)
= 1 - 1 + b
= b
